item.title: CVE-2016-2983|2024-09-17T01:01:43.379Z -- ibm -- tealeaf%20customer%20experience
item.description: IBM Tealeaf Customer Experience 8.7, 8.8, and 9.0.2 could allow a remote attacker under unusual circumstances to read operational data or TLS session state for any active sessions, cause denial of service, or bypass security. IBM X-Force ID: 113999.
